SELECT 
  time + interval '10s' as time,
  sub.pct as "pct",
  sub.transaction as "metric"
FROM (SELECT  time_bucket('10s', "timestamp") as time,
  max(pct95) as "pct",
  concat('PCT 95 ', thread_group_name, ' ', name, ' ', test_id) as "transaction"
  FROM jmeter_metrics.sample_metric
  WHERE
  timestamp BETWEEN '2024-08-30T13:50:49.608Z' AND '2024-08-30T14:50:49.608Z' AND
  (-9999 in ('18860') OR test_id in ('18860')) AND
  is_transaction in (true, false) AND
  ('%%all%%' in ('%%all%%') OR location IN ('%%all%%'))
  GROUP BY 1, thread_group_name, name, test_id
  ORDER BY 1
) sub

SELECT 
  at.time + interval '10s' as "time", 
  sum(at.threads) as "threads",
  concat('Threads ', test_id) as "metric"
FROM (
  SELECT 
  time_bucket('10s', "timestamp") as time,
  locf(last(threads, timestamp)) as "threads",
  test_id
  FROM jmeter_metrics.thread_metric
  WHERE
  timestamp BETWEEN '2024-08-30T13:50:49.608Z' AND '2024-08-30T14:50:49.608Z' AND
  (-9999 in ('18860') OR test_id in ('18860')) AND
  ('%%all%%' in ('%%all%%') OR location IN ('%%all%%'))
  GROUP BY 1, test_id, container_id
  ORDER BY 1
) at
GROUP BY 1, test_id
ORDER BY 1
